1
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:29,660
♪In the stormy night♪

2
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,340
♪The dark hair of a charming woman
is reflected in the flame of a candle♪

3
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,300
♪Shrouded by
year after year of memories♪

4
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,780
I can do nothing but feign indifference

5
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:53,140
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

6
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,540
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

7
00:00:55,740 --> 00:00:57,420
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself♪

8
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:01,140
♪Rebuild or crumble♪

9
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:03,780
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

10
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,660
♪Driving away♪

11
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:09,300
♪Your dashing pretense♪

12
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:11,620
♪A drunken dream♪

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,500
♪A person I miss♪

14
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,860
♪Of course I know if it's real♪

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:21,660
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

16
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:28,220
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

17
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:35,060
[In Blossom]

18
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:38,740
[Episode 2]

19
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:45,020
[Li Mansion]

20
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,800
Why is Mr. Pan here?

21
00:01:48,830 --> 00:01:49,720
I don't know.

22
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,270
They're from the Silver Rain Terrace.

23
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,590
What is going on here?

24
00:01:55,630 --> 00:01:57,080
I don't know either.

25
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:58,910
This is terrible.

26
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,910
You murderer.

27
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,950
How dare you show up here.

28
00:02:11,390 --> 00:02:12,160
Ze.

29
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:14,880
Today is the seventh day
after Mr. Li's death.

30
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:17,110
Do behave yourself at the mourning hall.

31
00:02:17,110 --> 00:02:17,800
Yes, Mr. Pan.

32
00:02:20,270 --> 00:02:22,550
I heard there is a funeral
in the Silver Rain Terrace today.

33
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:26,670
We should be kind to visitors
regardless of grudges.

34
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,800
Just look at
how you treat your visitors.

35
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:33,830
Mr. Li was a respectable figure.

36
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:35,240
I have always admired him.

37
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:37,270
So I'm here to pay my respects to him

38
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,880
for the last time.

39
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,800
Mr. Chen, I seek for your approval

40
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,240
on this.

41
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,600
They're visitors after all.

42
00:02:53,670 --> 00:02:54,750
We'll spare her life

43
00:02:55,830 --> 00:02:57,160
for today.

44
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,600
This way, please.

45
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,470
Seriously, are you
sure enough about this?

46
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,360
A little bit.

47
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:15,470
Mr. Li.

48
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,030
It's been several years,

49
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,030
but we have met only once.

50
00:03:20,030 --> 00:03:21,360
You know well

51
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,360
who's behind your death.

52
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,960
You can tell me in my dream.

53
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:27,600
I'll definitely do something for you.

54
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,160
Mr. Li.

55
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:45,670
Are you talking?

56
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,360
Alright.

57
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:48,470
I'm all ears.

58
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,800
Mr. Li has indeed had an unjust death.

59
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:55,520
What did he say?

60
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:57,720
He said

61
00:03:58,670 --> 00:04:00,110
the murderer is here,

62
00:04:00,910 --> 00:04:02,320
among these people.

63
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,360
You are really here to cause a scene.

64
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,160
Get this girl

65
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,000
as the sacrifice to Mr. Li!

66
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:09,720
Stop it!

67
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,700
[Memorial Tablet of Li Shanjiang]

68
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,320
Sir.

69
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,760
[Sun Zhen,
the head of Silver Rain Terrace]

70
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:38,320
I'm Sun Zhen,
the head of Silver Rain Terrace.

71
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:40,720
So, you're the censorate, Pan Yue?

72
00:04:40,790 --> 00:04:41,440
Yes, I am.

73
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:44,160
I'm glad you're here in time.

74
00:04:44,550 --> 00:04:46,350
Otherwise,

75
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,510
I'd be killed here today.

76
00:04:49,670 --> 00:04:51,920
You swaggered all the way here

77
00:04:52,390 --> 00:04:55,160
just to make the person in charge of
Silver Rain Terrace show up, no?

78
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,830
In that case, let me make things clear.

79
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,480
I'm here today

80
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:02,040
to investigate the case
of the murder of the Li family.

81
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:04,200
The murderer is this ugly woman
standing right next to you.

82
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:04,950
What else do you want to investigate?

83
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,880
I heard dogs only bark

84
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,230
when they are scared.

85
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,600
Who are you calling a dog?

86
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:12,000
The one who is scared.

87
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:13,350
You...

88
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,950
You're the head of Silver Rain Terrace.

89
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:22,550
I believe that you don't think

90
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,640
that this fragile lady

91
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,790
is the real culprit of the tragedy.

92
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,390
This is just nonsense.

93
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,510
Fine.

94
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,600
You may perform the investigation.

95
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:36,000
This way, please.

96
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:55,790
Don't you want to find out the truth?

97
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,790
Pull yourself together.

98
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:20,470
[Memorial Tablet of Li Lang]

99
00:06:20,470 --> 00:06:21,370
[Memorial Tablet of Li Shanjiang]

100
00:06:21,370 --> 00:06:22,220
[Memorial Tablet of Li's wife, Zhao]

101
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:30,830
What's wrong?

102
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,000
There's no beef in her stomach.

103
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,600
I found

104
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,830
the culprit who killed
Mr. Li and his family,

105
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,640
Xiazhong Grass.

106
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:55,390
The murderer put it into the beef.

107
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:57,270
Everyone in the Li family
took it one after another.

108
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,000
Having consumed the Xiazhong Grass,

109
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,640
they felt severe pain
in their internal organs.

110
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,440
They couldn't take the pain

111
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,830
and lost their mind gradually.

112
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:06,160
Hence, one by one,
they chose to commit suicide.

113
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,790
The murderer hid a rattle drum
and a mouse

114
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,320
in the beams.

115
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:17,790
The rumors about the rattle drum

116
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,710
were used to convince others

117
00:07:19,710 --> 00:07:21,670
that these people were killed by a ghost.

118
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,390
I suspected the murderer

119
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,350
to be the foe of Silver Rain Terrace.

120
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:29,350
But when I examined
the bodies last night,

121
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:31,270
a group of masked men
were trying to assassinate me.

122
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,480
Unfortunately,

123
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:35,920
I found this on them.

124
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,480
Silver Rain Terrace
wouldn't have their assassins

125
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,760
put on black clothes and masks
for a mission.

126
00:07:43,110 --> 00:07:44,270
This means

127
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,720
he has to keep his identity secret.

128
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,720
And in the Silver Rain Terrace,

129
00:07:47,790 --> 00:07:48,890
the one who has

130
00:07:48,890 --> 00:07:50,510
a direct interest-based relationship
with Mr. Li

131
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,350
is none other than...

132
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,880
What do you mean?

133
00:08:01,790 --> 00:08:03,390
Sir, he's slandering me.

134
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,600
Mr. Li and I were like brothers.

135
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,390
Why would I do such a treacherous thing?

136
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,390
Mr. Chen.

137
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:10,000
Don't get so worked up yet.

138
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,320
Before coming here,

139
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,760
I've checked about you.

140
00:08:14,550 --> 00:08:16,320
You have taken over

141
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,830
from the late Mr. Li.

142
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,760
After the funeral,

143
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:22,160
you will be promoted to leader.

144
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:22,880
Am I right?

145
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:24,110
So what?

146
00:08:24,790 --> 00:08:27,200
Mr. Li was most concerned about
our terrace when he was alive.

147
00:08:27,550 --> 00:08:28,550
I'm doing this

148
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:30,670
to make sure Mr. Li

149
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,790
can rest in peace as soon as possible.

150
00:08:33,710 --> 00:08:35,230
You're so considerate.

151
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:37,320
This is really touching.

152
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:40,760
If Mr. Li knew

153
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,440
that some of his private residences

154
00:08:42,470 --> 00:08:44,350
had also been transferred
under your name,

155
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:47,910
I wonder if he could
still rest in peace.

156
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,400
Pan.

157
00:08:52,470 --> 00:08:53,790
Stop making false accusations.

158
00:08:54,710 --> 00:08:56,080
Show us your evidence.

159
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,790
A few properties prove nothing.

160
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:00,670
If you can't find any evidence,

161
00:09:01,350 --> 00:09:02,910
I don't care who you are.

162
00:09:03,110 --> 00:09:03,790
I'll kill you!

163
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:04,590
I have the evidence.

164
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:09,400
When hands are contaminated
with the poison of Xiazhong Grass,

165
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,640
they will turn black
when they come in contact with water.

166
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,030
Mr. Chen,

167
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:15,230
do you dare do the test here and now?

168
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,000
Who do you think you are?

169
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,400
Why should I listen to you?

170
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:20,280
Do it now.

171
00:09:23,710 --> 00:09:24,960
Alright, then.

172
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:55,350
What now?

173
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:56,320
Do my hands turn black?

174
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,520
What else do you have to say now?

175
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,150
Mr. Chen.

176
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:11,440
How do you get
the scratches on your arm?

177
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,350
What does it have to do with you?

178
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,280
It's because

179
00:10:18,710 --> 00:10:19,790
I said

180
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:22,080
Xiazhong Grass turns the hands black
when it comes in contact with water.

181
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,590
But I lied to you on purpose.

182
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,840
The scratch on your arm

183
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,710
is the evidence I've been looking for.

184
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:33,960
Everyone,

185
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,400
take a look at the maid's nails.

186
00:10:40,470 --> 00:10:42,200
When I was examining
the corpse just now,

187
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:44,640
I found
that only her stomach doesn't have beef.

188
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:49,470
There's no beef in her stomach.

189
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,350
She was strangled to death from behind.

190
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:57,150
And the killer made it look like
she committed suicide.

191
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:00,470
You bribed the maid to poison the beef,

192
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:02,550
and you wanted to kill her after that.

193
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,470
She struggled to death.

194
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,590
The scratches should be on the arm.

195
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:10,400
The green and red inks from your skin
found under her nails

196
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,760
are unique to the Silver Rain Terrace.

197
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,550
All of you must be
very familiar with it.

198
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,880
I don't need to say much about it.

199
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:16,640
Mr. Chen.

200
00:11:17,110 --> 00:11:19,030
You killed nine people of the Li family

201
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:20,550
and the evidence is clear now.

202
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:22,150
You can no longer deny it.

203
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:27,640
Did you try to fool me?

204
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:35,840
If I'm dead,

205
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:39,000
you can't live either.

206
00:12:29,590 --> 00:12:30,200
Wait.

207
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:12,840
What's wrong with you?

208
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:17,470
I've seen too many corpses

209
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:19,320
dumped in the mass graves.

210
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:22,550
Those people lived happily

211
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,710
but died without dignity.

212
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:27,350
I have thought

213
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,840
if I knew the time I would die,

214
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,660
I must
find a beautiful peach blossom forest

215
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:33,710
in advance

216
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,320
for the burial of my body.

217
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:38,840
That forest looks quite good.

218
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:42,550
Although there are only a few trees now,

219
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:43,910
in another month,

220
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:46,790
thousands of peach blossoms will be
in full bloom, bright, and red like fire.

221
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:48,910
Pink peach blossoms

222
00:13:49,710 --> 00:13:51,350
will be all over the mountain.

223
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,320
You are still the same
as when you were a child,

224
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:57,670
you still like peach blossoms.

225
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,520
Yes,

226
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:02,400
when I was a kid, I watched...

227
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:10,200
Don't need to cover it anymore,

228
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,320
I already looked into it.

229
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:15,550
Ten years ago,

230
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,760
your father was convicted and exiled.

231
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:20,200
He encountered robbers on the road.

232
00:14:20,590 --> 00:14:21,640
Both of your parents died.

233
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:23,200
You fled to Heyang

234
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:24,710
and were adopted by Mr. Jiang.

235
00:14:25,760 --> 00:14:26,550
Eight years ago,

236
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,760
you started working
as Mr. Jiang's assistant.

237
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:30,230
Five years ago,

238
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,280
Mr. Jiang's madness was getting worse.

239
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:33,960
He was dismissed from the county yamen.

240
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,960
You started working and moving bodies
at the Coffin Home.

241
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,080
And you've taken care of him
until this day.

242
00:14:37,710 --> 00:14:38,960
Do you want me to continue?

243
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:48,350
Why were you looking for me?

244
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:52,030
I want you to be
the real Yang Caiwei again.

245
00:15:04,640 --> 00:15:05,790
The engagement
granted by the late emperor,

246
00:15:06,230 --> 00:15:07,280
we are related by marriage.

247
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,640
My second condition is

248
00:15:10,710 --> 00:15:11,520
I want to marry you.

249
00:15:52,350 --> 00:15:53,520
Miss Shangguan.

250
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:56,000
You've pursued slim beauty too much

251
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,280
and hurt the fundamentals.

252
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,840
Let me carefully condition your body.

253
00:16:18,880 --> 00:16:21,760
I am willing to endure any pain for you.

254
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:23,470
Pan.

255
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:27,110
We are a match made in heaven.

256
00:16:36,460 --> 00:16:39,100
[Shangguan Zhi,
Young Lady of Shangguan Family]

257
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:48,300
[Shangguan Family Account Book]

258
00:17:02,710 --> 00:17:03,320
Zhi.

259
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:05,000
Why are you here?

260
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:06,310
Shouldn't you attend

261
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:07,880
the tea class at this time?

262
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:11,400
Look,

263
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,230
the wind is blowing strong out here.

264
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:14,640
And you are not wearing enough layers.

265
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,280
You might catch a cold later.

266
00:17:17,040 --> 00:17:18,230
Yue has been missing for two days,

267
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:19,230
I'm worried.

268
00:17:19,950 --> 00:17:20,710
Lan,

269
00:17:21,310 --> 00:17:22,710
I asked you to inquire
about his whereabouts before,

270
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:23,590
is there any news?

271
00:17:24,430 --> 00:17:25,310
Don't worry.

272
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:26,830
Someone has been sent to look for him.

273
00:17:27,110 --> 00:17:29,000
Shangguan family's businesses
are spread all over the world,

274
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:30,710
there should be news soon.

275
00:17:32,470 --> 00:17:34,830
I heard that the Pan Mansion
has been closed for the past two days.

276
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,070
I know

277
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:38,400
Yue showed his good interest
