00:32:38,430 --> 00:32:39,350
He painted it blindly.

555
00:32:41,760 --> 00:32:42,560
Blindly?

556
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,000
But the painting is quite good.

557
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:49,400
One has a scar on the face,

558
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:51,760
and the other
carries a wound in the heart.

559
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:56,590
They should have been a perfect match.

560
00:32:57,230 --> 00:32:58,760
It's a pity.

561
00:32:59,560 --> 00:33:00,680
Such a pity.

562
00:33:01,310 --> 00:33:02,680
We're reaching
the end of Ghost Market.

563
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:04,590
Why haven't we seen
the person selling the Spirit Snake yet?

564
00:33:07,830 --> 00:33:08,640
Xiaosheng!

565
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:09,830
Caiwei!

566
00:33:13,830 --> 00:33:14,760
You're here.

567
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:20,230
What are you looking at?

568
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:21,680
[Bai Xiaosheng,
vendor in Ghost Market]

569
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:22,760
This man is...

570
00:33:24,190 --> 00:33:25,830
He's our apprentice at the Coffin Home,

571
00:33:25,950 --> 00:33:27,000
and he hasn't seen much of the world.

572
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:28,640
Today, I brought him here
to broaden his horizons.

573
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:41,760
His physique is all right.

574
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,950
Can he carry a body?

575
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:44,760
Yes, he can.

576
00:33:45,190 --> 00:33:46,230
You still need more practice.

577
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:47,400
Don't mess things up for Miss Yang.

578
00:33:47,470 --> 00:33:48,110
Exactly.

579
00:33:49,560 --> 00:33:50,640
Listen to her, practice more.

580
00:33:51,350 --> 00:33:52,000
Xiaosheng,

581
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:53,470
has the Spirit Snake catcher
arrived yet?

582
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:55,470
He's here.
I've been keeping an eye out for you.

583
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:56,880
But

584
00:33:57,280 --> 00:33:58,070
the old guy

585
00:33:58,110 --> 00:33:59,640
is quite the drinker.

586
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:02,070
I don't know where he is right now.

587
00:34:02,280 --> 00:34:03,280
All right,

588
00:34:03,590 --> 00:34:05,070
now even my money is on the line.

589
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:06,520
Here, take it.

590
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,560
Take everything you want.

591
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:08,560
Just kidding.

592
00:34:08,670 --> 00:34:10,080
We share a bond of asking for meals,

593
00:34:10,190 --> 00:34:11,360
so how could I take your money for real?

594
00:34:11,760 --> 00:34:14,600
That old guy is probably lounging
by the river, getting drunk.

595
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:15,430
I'll take you to find him.

596
00:34:15,430 --> 00:34:16,150
All right. Let's go.

597
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:17,670
Move.

598
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:33,140
[Sunrise Garden]

599
00:34:33,470 --> 00:34:34,840
This is Mr. Pan's residence.

600
00:34:35,080 --> 00:34:36,230
Unauthorized people
are not allowed to disturb.

601
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:36,800
Leave.

602
00:34:36,870 --> 00:34:37,800
Take a good look.

603
00:34:38,040 --> 00:34:40,040
Is Young Lady
an unauthorized person here?

604
00:34:43,230 --> 00:34:44,230
Miss Shangguan.

605
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,040
Miss Shangguan.

606
00:35:11,870 --> 00:35:12,760
Miss Shangguan.

607
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:16,430
What's wrong, Miss Shangguan?

608
00:35:16,430 --> 00:35:16,870
Scram!

609
00:35:17,430 --> 00:35:19,040
- Noted.
- Noted.

610
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,800
Wake up, sir.

611
00:35:32,870 --> 00:35:33,520
It's time for business.

612
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:34,390
I want to buy a Spotted Spirit Snake.

613
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,520
Want to buy Spotted Spirit Snake?

614
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:37,040
Yes.

615
00:35:38,430 --> 00:35:39,950
You're lucky.

616
00:35:41,950 --> 00:35:43,360
Let me show you something.

617
00:35:49,230 --> 00:35:49,840
This...

618
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:53,470
This Spotted Spirit Snake
hides in the snowy mountains,

619
00:35:53,870 --> 00:35:56,600
only revealing itself
when the snow melts.

620
00:35:57,710 --> 00:35:59,000
You won't find another one like this

621
00:35:59,080 --> 00:36:00,950
in the entire Ghost Market.

622
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:02,840
Don't raise the price.
Just tell me how much you're selling it.

623
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:05,800
Fifty guan,

624
00:36:06,080 --> 00:36:07,150
not a wen less.

625
00:36:07,190 --> 00:36:07,870
Sir,

626
00:36:08,430 --> 00:36:09,600
last time we agreed

627
00:36:09,670 --> 00:36:10,710
on ten guan.

628
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:11,800
Ten?

629
00:36:11,870 --> 00:36:12,360
Right.

630
00:36:12,430 --> 00:36:13,360
Don't you remember me?

631
00:36:14,390 --> 00:36:16,560
Circumstances change.

632
00:36:18,040 --> 00:36:19,950
I spent over a month
in the snowy mountains

633
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:21,280
to catch this one,

634
00:36:21,390 --> 00:36:23,800
and I froze my leg doing it.

635
00:36:24,910 --> 00:36:27,080
I won't be able to go back
to the snowy mountains after this.

636
00:36:27,150 --> 00:36:28,190
I have to make up

637
00:36:28,390 --> 00:36:29,840
the medical expenses

638
00:36:29,910 --> 00:36:31,150
from this, right?

639
00:36:35,870 --> 00:36:36,560
Enough, right?

640
00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:39,720
Yes, enough.

641
00:36:40,560 --> 00:36:41,560
I don't deserve it.

642
00:36:41,870 --> 00:36:43,470
I'll figure out my own affairs.

643
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:44,150
You...

644
00:36:45,430 --> 00:36:46,080
Sir,

645
00:36:46,150 --> 00:36:47,520
take this money first.

646
00:36:47,870 --> 00:36:48,630
I'll make up for it

647
00:36:48,710 --> 00:36:50,040
within a month.

648
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:51,120
For every day overdue,

649
00:36:51,870 --> 00:36:53,150
I'll add another guan.

650
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:54,390
All right.

651
00:36:54,600 --> 00:36:55,120
Sell it.

652
00:36:56,150 --> 00:36:57,360
All right,

653
00:36:57,430 --> 00:36:58,150
I'll sell it to you.

654
00:36:58,560 --> 00:37:00,080
Here, take this snake.

655
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,150
Thank you, sir.

656
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,360
It's just some silvers.

657
00:37:06,430 --> 00:37:07,950
Do we need to settle up so precisely?

658
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:08,840
It's better to settle things clearly

659
00:37:09,390 --> 00:37:10,430
since we met by chance.

660
00:37:13,560 --> 00:37:14,390
Who is he?

661
00:37:15,190 --> 00:37:16,520
Come, take a look.

662
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:17,320
It's him.

663
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:18,800
He's Pan Yue,

664
00:37:18,870 --> 00:37:20,190
the imperial censorate.

665
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:23,150
- Pan Yue?
- Pan Yue?

666
00:37:23,150 --> 00:37:24,120
What's he doing here?

667
00:37:25,390 --> 00:37:27,150
He's the Pan Yue who wants to marry you?

668
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:28,080
Yes.

669
00:37:30,300 --> 00:37:31,310
Who is this guy?

670
00:37:31,430 --> 00:37:32,230
Sir,

671
00:37:32,470 --> 00:37:34,000
do you still want
to conceal your identity?

672
00:37:37,150 --> 00:37:37,670
Pan Yue.

673
00:37:37,950 --> 00:37:38,910
Who is he?

674
00:37:45,150 --> 00:37:46,840
Ghost Market isn't for officials.

675
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:48,000
Put down your stuff

676
00:37:48,120 --> 00:37:48,910
and leave quickly.

677
00:37:50,190 --> 00:37:51,390
I came to the Ghost Market
to buy things.

678
00:37:51,430 --> 00:37:52,120
There's nothing to do with him.

679
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:53,800
Give it to me.

680
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:57,520
Let go of me.

681
00:38:07,230 --> 00:38:08,150
Spirit Snake.

682
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:09,430
Caiwei!

683
00:38:12,390 --> 00:38:13,230
- What are you doing?
- Let go!

684
00:38:13,390 --> 00:38:13,870
The Spirit Snake!

685
00:38:13,950 --> 00:38:15,360
Are you crazy?
The river is full of knives.

686
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:18,120
The Spirit Snake is gone.
I can't save Master.

687
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:20,390
What should I do?

688
00:38:21,230 --> 00:38:21,950
The Spirit Snake...

689
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:26,430
He really jumped into it.

690
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:27,230
Pan Yue!

691
00:38:27,630 --> 00:38:29,320
Is he out of his mind?

692
00:38:29,950 --> 00:38:30,560
So amazing.

693
00:38:30,910 --> 00:38:31,840
He really risked his life.

694
00:38:32,630 --> 00:38:33,800
Yes, it's so dangerous.

695
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,280
He's got guts.

696
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:37,800
The river has knives in it.

697
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:40,430
Looks like the thing
is really important to him.

698
00:38:42,390 --> 00:38:43,360
You're right.

699
00:39:17,470 --> 00:39:18,060
Pan Yue.

700
00:39:21,100 --> 00:39:22,140
He's really brave.

701
00:39:23,910 --> 00:39:26,000
No movement. Is he dead?

702
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:27,190
- Shut up.
- Stop it.

703
00:39:31,430 --> 00:39:32,470
Pan Yue.

704
00:39:37,670 --> 00:39:38,760
Pan Yue.

705
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,150
Why is there still no movement?

706
00:39:43,470 --> 00:39:44,190
Is he all right?

707
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,360
He's out.

708
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:47,150
Pan Yue.

709
00:39:50,080 --> 00:39:50,760
I got it.

710
00:39:53,910 --> 00:39:54,560
He got it.

711
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:56,280
- Yes.
- That's amazing.

712
00:39:56,910 --> 00:39:58,120
So brave.

713
00:39:58,320 --> 00:40:00,560
He isn't an ordinary person.

714
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:02,760
- Yes.
- Right.

715
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,190
Mr. Pan,

716
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,760
I'm grateful

717
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:22,840
for your help,

718
00:40:24,560 --> 00:40:26,430
but Heyang is not where you should be.

719
00:40:27,120 --> 00:40:28,080
Ten years ago,

720
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:31,080
you had someone tell me
to sever ties with you.

721
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,560
We've been strangers since then.

722
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:36,630
Regardless of whether

723
00:40:37,470 --> 00:40:38,910
you're here on a whim

724
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:42,190
or out of guilt,

725
00:40:42,470 --> 00:40:43,760
it doesn't matter anymore.

726
00:40:44,390 --> 00:40:45,870
Let bygones be bygones.

727
00:40:47,870 --> 00:40:48,760
It ends here.

728
00:40:49,520 --> 00:40:50,040
Is that all right?

729
00:40:51,670 --> 00:40:52,360
Yang Caiwei,

730
00:40:56,230 --> 00:40:57,670
you're not as heartless toward me

731
00:40:58,120 --> 00:40:59,390
as you claim,

732
00:41:00,950 --> 00:41:01,760
are you?

733
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:08,190
I never knew you came to me back then.

734
00:41:10,120 --> 00:41:12,320
Whatever was said to you
by the person at my door,

735
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,760
it was probably on my father's orders.

736
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:16,800
Over the years,

737
00:41:16,800 --> 00:41:18,710
I'd been searching for news
about you everywhere.

738
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:20,150
When I found out you were in Heyang,

739
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,760
I rushed here immediately.

740
00:41:22,470 --> 00:41:23,520
I thought

741
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:25,280
fulfilling the marriage contract

742
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:27,470
would be the best way for me
to make it up to you.

743
00:41:29,670 --> 00:41:31,560
But I've overlooked all

744
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:33,470
that you've been through
over these years,

745
00:41:35,670 --> 00:41:37,080
and I have no idea

746
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,080
what you truly want now.

747
00:41:41,390 --> 00:41:41,950
I'm sorry.

748
00:41:42,670 --> 00:41:44,150
I was too presumptuous.

749
00:41:53,950 --> 00:41:54,630
Mr. Pan,

750
00:41:56,910 --> 00:41:58,760
we're no longer from the same world.

751
00:41:59,950 --> 00:42:01,840
Since you've found me today,

752
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:06,390
consider
your unfulfilled promises settled.

753
00:42:09,230 --> 00:42:10,950
Let's leave the past behind us.

754
00:42:11,670 --> 00:42:12,390
We need not mention it again

755
00:42:13,360 --> 00:42:14,000
in the future.

756
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:15,040
But I want to.

757
00:42:17,040 --> 00:42:17,800
I came to find you

758
00:42:18,360 --> 00:42:20,080
not just to fulfill
the marriage contract

759
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:22,840
but because I want to find you,

760
00:42:22,950 --> 00:42:24,670
take care of you, and protect you.

761
00:42:25,870 --> 00:42:27,080
Whether it's ten years ago

762
00:42:27,470 --> 00:42:28,520
or ten years from now,

763
00:42:29,630 --> 00:42:30,950
you're the only person

764
00:42:31,560 --> 00:42:32,710
I want to marry in this lifetime.

765
00:42:38,870 --> 00:42:39,870
I'll still be waiting for you

766
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:42,560
on our wedding day,

767
00:42:43,670 --> 00:42:44,560
but whether you show up or not

768
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:46,630
is entirely up to you.

769
00:42:59,500 --> 00:43:04,980
[Sunrise Garden]

770
00:43:04,980 --> 00:43:10,600
[Exceptional Appearance and Intellect]

771
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:12,630
Mr. Pan, you're finally back.

772
00:43:12,760 --> 00:43:14,000
We couldn't stop

773
00:43:14,520 --> 00:43:15,710
Miss Shangguan at all.

774
00:43:27,150 --> 00:43:28,080
What are you doing?

775
00:43:32,230 --> 00:43:33,040
Yue,

776
00:43:34,190 --> 00:43:35,760
are you really going
to marry that ugly woman?

777
00:43:36,390 --> 00:43:38,560
Yang Caiwei is the woman
I'm going to marry soon.

778
00:43:38,910 --> 00:43:40,150
Please respect her.

779
00:43:41,280 --> 00:43:42,000
What about me, then?

780
00:43:42,760 --> 00:43:43,630
What am I?

781
00:43:44,230 --> 00:43:45,760
I've told you many times.

782
00:43:46,670 --> 00:43:48,520
I only see you
as Shangguan Lan's sister.

783
00:43:49,190 --> 00:43:50,560
There are no romantic feelings involved.

784
00:43:51,040 --> 00:43:51,800
No way.

785
00:43:52,390 --> 00:43:53,800
I can't believe
I'm losing to someone like her.

786
00:43:56,760 --> 00:43:57,800
You must be marrying her

787
00:43:58,840 --> 00:44:00,670
because of the marriage contract.

788
00:44:01,630 --> 00:44:02,320
Yue,

789
00:44:03,390 --> 00:44:04,870
I don't care about status.

790
00:44:05,870 --> 00:44:06,950
I can be a concubine.

791
00:44:08,430 --> 00:44:09,560
You just won't listen to me.

792
00:44:09,760 --> 00:44:10,470
Pan Yue!

793
00:44:13,040 --> 00:44:13,840
Yue,

794
00:44:15,080 --> 00:44:15,950
do you know

795
00:44:16,840 --> 00:44:18,150
how much I've endured

796
00:44:18,190 --> 00:44:19,120
for a perfect body

797
00:44:19,190 --> 00:44:20,630
just to stand by your side?

798
00:44:21,520 --> 00:44:22,800
I've suffered so much pain.

799
00:44:23,360 --> 00:44:25,470
Everything I've done has been for you.

800
00:44:35,120 --> 00:44:35,870
Shangguan Zhi,

801
00:44:36,910 --> 00:44:38,280
the appearance you're so obsessed with

802
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:40,230
has never been what I wanted.

803
00:44:40,600 --> 00:44:42,120
The inner beauty
is more important than appearance.

804
00:44:42,430 --> 00:44:43,630
You'll meet your true love,

805
00:44:44,840 --> 00:44:45,710
but that person

806
00:44:46,630 --> 00:44:47,390
isn't me.

807
00:44:58,180 --> 00:45:00,180
[Coffin Home]

808
00:45:47,710 --> 00:45:49,840
I never knew you came to me back then.

809
00:45:51,600 --> 00:45:53,870
Whatever was said to you
by the person at my door,

810
00:45:54,560 --> 00:45:56,470
it was probably on my father's orders.

811
00:45:56,800 --> 00:45:57,760
I'll still be waiting for you

812
00:45:59,190 --> 00:46:00,470
on our wedding day,

813
00:46:01,360 --> 00:46:02,390
but whether you show up or not

814
00:46:03,800 --> 00:46:04,430
is entirely up to you.

815
00:46:49,870 --> 00:46:50,560
Coming.

816
00:46:54,910 --> 00:46:55,870
Coming, coming.

817
00:46:57,630 --> 00:46:58,320
Coming.

818
00:47:16,870 --> 00:47:18,320
A woman is dead.

819
00:47:18,710 --> 00:47:20,430
Her body needs
to be brought over for storage.

820
00:47:23,100 --> 00:47:32,900
[Coffin Home]

821
00:47:35,760 --> 00:47:36,840
How did she die?

822
00:47:41,150 --> 00:47:42,630
Spiritually dead.

823
00:48:21,390 --> 00:48:22,150
Where am I?

824
00:48:23,630 --> 00:48:24,870
Who are you?

825
00:48:26,760 --> 00:48:27,710
Why did you tie me up?

826
00:48:27,800 --> 00:48:28,630
Let me go!

827
00:48:43,190 --> 00:48:44,430
So ugly.

828
00:48:45,560 --> 00:48:47,560
I want to slash your face
a couple of times,

829
00:48:47,870 --> 00:48:48,950
but I can't find a place.

830
00:48:50,120 --> 00:48:51,040
I...

831
00:48:51,600 --> 00:48:52,630
I'm ugly,

832
00:48:53,560 --> 00:48:55,120
but I've never provoked you.

833
00:48:56,430 --> 00:48:57,150
Let me go.

834
00:48:57,840 --> 00:48:58,600
I... I promise

835
00:48:58,950 --> 00:49:00,280
I'll stay far away.

836
00:49:02,600 --> 00:49:03,360
You know,

837
00:49:04,560 --> 00:49:05,870
what I've endured

