863
00:50:09,190 --> 00:50:10,520
It's a win-win, isn't it?

864
00:50:10,760 --> 00:50:11,950
Do you think I'll believe you?

865
00:50:13,950 --> 00:50:15,630
I know Yue too well.

866
00:50:17,390 --> 00:50:19,470
His heart is as firm as a rock.

867
00:50:20,150 --> 00:50:21,800
Once he decides something,

868
00:50:22,040 --> 00:50:23,080
he never changes it.

869
00:50:24,360 --> 00:50:25,470
If he says he's marrying you,

870
00:50:26,190 --> 00:50:27,470
then he's marrying you.

871
00:50:30,320 --> 00:50:31,320
Shangguan Zhi,

872
00:50:31,910 --> 00:50:33,470
what are you up to?

873
00:50:34,150 --> 00:50:35,190
For him,

874
00:50:36,000 --> 00:50:37,600
I can become more and more beautiful,

875
00:50:39,470 --> 00:50:40,560
and I can endure everything

876
00:50:40,600 --> 00:50:41,600
that disgusts me,

877
00:50:41,670 --> 00:50:42,280
including

878
00:50:44,470 --> 00:50:45,950
a disgusting face.

879
00:50:56,950 --> 00:50:57,840
Shangguan Zhi,

880
00:50:59,800 --> 00:51:00,760
what are you doing?

881
00:51:01,320 --> 00:51:02,150
Don't touch me!

882
00:51:15,230 --> 00:51:15,670
No...

883
00:51:16,280 --> 00:51:16,910
No...

884
00:51:17,040 --> 00:51:17,840
Shangguan Zhi,

885
00:51:18,670 --> 00:51:19,670
