886
00:51:20,000 --> 00:51:21,280
What are you trying to do?

887
00:51:23,040 --> 00:51:24,560
From today,

888
00:51:25,470 --> 00:51:28,150
I'll take your place as Mrs. Pan,

889
00:51:28,710 --> 00:51:30,560
and you'll take mine,

890
00:51:33,360 --> 00:51:34,800
someone who commits suicide for love.

891
00:51:35,630 --> 00:51:37,000
The coffin is ready for you.

892
00:51:42,520 --> 00:51:43,630
To my surprise,

893
00:51:45,600 --> 00:51:47,120
the chubby girl I hadn't seen in years

894
00:51:47,840 --> 00:51:49,430
had become so malicious.

895
00:51:51,670 --> 00:51:52,710
But listen here,

896
00:51:53,520 --> 00:51:54,760
no matter what you do,

897
00:51:55,320 --> 00:51:57,710
it'll all be in vain.

898
00:51:58,320 --> 00:52:00,000
Pan Yue won't marry you.

899
00:52:01,840 --> 00:52:02,950
You're so vile.

900
00:52:03,670 --> 00:52:04,950
It'll only disgust him.

901
00:52:05,120 --> 00:52:06,840
He won't even look at you.

902
00:52:11,870 --> 00:52:12,470
Don't come any closer,

903
00:52:12,600 --> 00:52:13,560
or I'll kill her.

904
00:52:13,760 --> 00:52:14,710
Let go of Young Lady.

905
00:52:15,800 --> 00:52:16,360
Move.

906
00:52:19,710 --> 00:52:20,430
Don't come any closer.

907
00:52:21,150 --> 00:52:21,800
If you do,

908
00:52:21,870 --> 00:52:22,760
I'll kill her.

909
00:52:24,150 --> 00:52:25,040
Yang Caiwei,

910
00:52:25,800 --> 00:52:26,950
