931
00:54:16,800 --> 00:54:17,600
Pan Yue,

932
00:54:19,230 --> 00:54:20,280
I like you,

933
00:54:20,800 --> 00:54:21,870
and I want to marry you.

934
00:54:22,870 --> 00:54:23,630
At this moment,

935
00:54:24,360 --> 00:54:26,080
our wedding is the most important thing.

936
00:54:26,870 --> 00:54:27,760
Everything else

937
00:54:28,320 --> 00:54:29,390
doesn't matter.

938
00:54:33,020 --> 00:54:35,020
